  "heading_path": "热力学第一定律 / 气体的热容与摩尔热容",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 95,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02959:7b829ba10326]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02960:006a82c9882e]] \n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02961:fb71037690ec]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02962:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02963:fb265bb08056]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02964:d34d4e215f26]] 等容：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02965:a791185e30d3]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02966:d711827ac22a]] 等温：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02967:15eb4bbdd338]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02968:0b6a24eb13fd]] 等压：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02969:b3ae5d504aaa]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02970:7d0c1131817d]]\n总计：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02971:a42014b2254c]][[PROTECTED:F00001-P02972:acd45eb486d3]][[PROTECTED:F00001-P02973:4d51a400d59b]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02974:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02975:f7c87337a05c]]\n\n\n\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02976:9dbc37a2ffdd]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02977:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n初态物质的量满足\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02978:e77bf7157394]]\n等压过程有\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02979:785b538d2926]]\n等压功为\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02980:d208937512a4]]\n等体过程有\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02981:33a9d63130d2]]\n所以 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02982:3bd3b0a7b128]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02983:55f067a39505]]，两种过程中的功分别为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02984:43e49b50832f]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02985:e1b62c20cd10]]。同样升温 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02986:6d389c09ed29]]，等压过程还要膨胀对外做功，所以需要的热量比等体过程多，差值正好是 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02987:5f3fd69bbae7]]。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02988:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02989:62c72559074e]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02990:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n先看等温压缩。\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02991:18895e37d266]]\n故外界需做功大小为\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02992:558fbd77dc1e]] \n\n再看准静态绝热压缩。对氢气取\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02993:435b4c02c39c]]\n由绝热方程\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02994:00508ea99eb5]] \n于是\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02995:dd2e83090ca1]]\n因此绝热压缩需要的外功更大。等温压缩时气体能把部分能量放给外界，所以更[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02996:84548e88f54b]]；绝热压缩时热量出不去，外界所做的功更多地堆进内能，因此更费功。计算中要始终分清系统对外做功的符号和外界需做功的大小。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02997:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n",
  "mode": "REWRITE",
