  "read_only_context_before": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02949:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n由[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02950:df91b9d8bde2]]到[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02951:ccd2b4a0ba37]]内能增加[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02952:510a2efb6f84]]，[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02953:c4ca909f3e64]]温度相同，所以内能相同。从[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02954:df91b9d8bde2]]到[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02955:2a6f81ee6375]]吸热[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02956:3b39c5b4f5f4]]，所以必定对外做功[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02957:514264ce37e9]] \n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02958:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}",
